data.title: CampusFlow
data.description: CampusFlow is an innovative education management software designed to automate and streamline various academic processes in educational institutions. It is a system that manages student information, academic records, schedules, assignments, and communication between students, teachers, and administrators.

data.description: SIME - (Simple Image Editor) - A Next.js webapp simplifying image enhancement with intuitive filters and operations. Streamlined interface for quick and easy image refinement, ensuring professional-quality results.

data.title: OpenAi Chatbot
data.description: Objective was to develope a real-time chatbot application leveraging Node.js, Socket.io, MongoDB, and OpenAI's API for natural language processing. The application enables seamless communication, stores chat history, and integrates advanced language processing capabilities.
